      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-spe-imp-000      thru vis-spe-imp-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Percentuali spese                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   vis-spe-per-000      thru vis-spe-per-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
