      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     vis-pie-reg-999.
       vis-pie-reg-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione prompts piede                             *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       pmt-pie-reg-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Erase linee impegnate                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Visualizzazione prompts                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Deviazione in funzione del numero pagina    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-pie-reg-100
                     pmt-pie-reg-200
                     depending            on   w-cnt-sts-imp-npp      .
           go to     pmt-pie-reg-999.
       pmt-pie-reg-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Trasporto a cura                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tra-cur-000      thru pmt-tra-cur-999        .
