           if        w-pie-tra-cur (1)    not  = 30
                     go to acc-cod-vt3-999.
           if        w-pie-cod-vt2 (1)    =    zero
                     go to acc-cod-vt3-999.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Salvataggio valore precedente               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-pie-cod-vt3 (1)    to   w-sav-cod-vet          .
       acc-cod-vt3-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
